ed="T" n="0801c29"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0801c29"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000057735"><placeName>襄州</placeName><placeName>辯覺寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A010902">清江</persName>傳</head><pb n="0802a" xml:id="T50.2061.0802a" ed="T"/><p><lb
ed="T" n="0802a01"/><persName key="A010902">釋清江</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000013239">會稽</placeName>人也，不詳氏族。幼悟幻泡<ptr type="glossary" target="#g567"/>，身<lb
ed="T" n="0802a02"/>拘<anchor xml:id="beg0802001"/>羈<anchor xml:id="end0802001"/>鞅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g569"/>，因入精舍，便戀空門，父母沮勸，建<lb
ed="T" n="0802a03"/>乎難拔。<anchor xml:id="beg0802sgsz1"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0802sgsz1"/><persName key="A004177">曇一<roleName>律主</roleName></persName>為親教師<ptr type="glossary" target="#g128"/>，諷誦經法，<lb
ed="T" n="0802a04"/>寓目<ptr type="glossary" target="#g572"/>俱通。長者品量之曰：「<name>釋</name>門千里駒也。」<lb
ed="T" n="0802a05"/>於<placeName key="PL000000008367">浙</placeName>陽<placeName key="PL000000011644">天竺</placeName>戒壇求法，與同學<persName key="A023320">清源</persName>從<persName key="A010894">守<lb
ed="T" n="0802a06"/>直<roleName>和尚</roleName></persName>下為弟子。還聽習<persName key="A004177">一<roleName>公</roleName></persName>《相疏》<ptr target="#n1737"/>并<persName key="A001519">南山</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0802a07"/>《律鈔》<ptr target="#n1290"/>。間歲<ptr type="glossary" target="#g575"/>，精義入神，舉皆通暢。而善篇章，<lb
ed="T" n="0802a08"/>儒家筆語，體高辭典，又擅一隅之美<ptr target="#n461"/>，時少倫<lb
ed="T" n="0802a09"/>儗。其褊懆<ptr type="glossary" target="#g579"/>之性，不與人類。嘗於<persName key="A004177">一<roleName>公</roleName></persName>少因<lb
ed="T" n="0802a10"/>不足，亦有捨和尚之譏。由是遊方服勤<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g837"/>，凡<lb
ed="T" n="0802a11"/>云律筵，無不預者。自責<anchor xml:id="beg0802sgsz3"/>己<anchor xml:id="end0802sgsz3"/>曰：「天下行半，少<lb
ed="T" n="0802a12"/>有如<ref type="person" target="#A004177">我本師</ref><ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g190"/>者。」還<placeName key="PL000000013239">會稽</placeName>，<persName key="A004177">一<roleName>公</roleName></persName>猶老，當其<lb
ed="T" n="0802a13"/>僧大集時，擊木唱：「<ref type="person" target="#A010902">某</ref>再投<ref type="person" target="#A004177">和尚</ref>攝受。」時<persName key="A004177">一<lb
ed="T" n="0802a14"/><roleName>公</roleName></persName>詬罵，<persName key="A010902">江</persName>雨淚而懺悔曰：「前念無知，後心有<lb
ed="T" n="0802a15"/>悟，望<ref type="person" target="#A004177">和尚</ref>大慈，施與歡喜。苟不許收，則<placeName key="PL000000011304">越</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0802a16"/>人不可以強售章甫也<ptr target="#n1738"/>。」<persName key="A004177">一<roleName>公</roleName></persName>憫其數四求<lb
ed="T" n="0802a17"/>哀，乃曰：「為<ref type="person" target="#A010902">汝</ref><anchor xml:id="beg0802sgsz5"/>含<anchor xml:id="end0802sgsz5"/>垢。」遂為師資<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1172"/>如初。<persName key="A010902">江</persName>有<lb
ed="T" n="0802a18"/>禪觀之學。<date from-iso="+0773-02-01" key="j20034242003806" to-iso="+0774-02-18"><name>大曆</name>八年</date>於<placeName key="PL000000026334">汝濆</placeName>遇<persName key="A001707">忠<roleName>國師</roleName></persName>，因<lb
ed="T" n="0802a19"/>弟子說自<persName key="A001707">忠</persName>曰：「此律師是和尚鄉人。」乃<lb
ed="T" n="0802a20"/>欣然相會，尋往<placeName key="PL000000025214">南陽</placeName>，再謁<persName key="A001707">國師</persName>，密傳心要<lb
ed="T" n="0802a21"/>焉。</p>
        <p xml:id="pT50p0802a2201"><lb
ed="T" n="0802a22"/>系曰：<persName key="A010902">江</persName>甞為《七夕詩》<ptr target="#n1739"/>，或謂之四背<ptr target="#n1740"/>中一背<lb
ed="T" n="0802a23"/>也。通曰：「詩人興詠，用意不倫。<persName key="A011067">慧休</persName>《怨別》<ptr target="#n1741"/>，<persName key="A006134">陸<lb
ed="T" n="0802a24"/>機</persName>《牽牛星》<ptr target="#n1742"/>，<persName key="A006021">屈原</persName>《湘夫人》<ptr target="#n1743"/>，豈為色邪？皆當時寓<lb
ed="T" n="0802a25"/>言興類而已。若然者，言火則焚口，說食則<lb
ed="T" n="0802a26"/>療飢也矣。<persName key="A010902">江</persName>之捨師，後乃揚師之美，反權<lb
ed="T" n="0802a27"/>合道<ptr target="#n1487"/>也。實為此詩警世無常，引令入佛<lb
ed="T" n="0802a28"/>智焉。其故何也？詳<persName key="A010902">江</persName>遇<persName key="A001707">忠<roleName>國師</roleName></persName>大明玄理，<lb
ed="T" n="0802a29"/>無以域中小乘法拘之哉！」</p>
